  "description": "So I\u0026rsquo;ve been using GnoponEmacs for a bit now and if I\u0026rsquo;m comparing my research method from before, when I was using Obsidian, to now, the method is so much better that it\u0026rsquo;s hard to even compare. So, great. I\u0026rsquo;m doing a lot better than I was, and in a way that shows a trajectory toward improving. I\u0026rsquo;m saying just because it can be easy, when taking a stance of criticism, critique, in order to improve, to feel that position: cultivated negativity that\u0026rsquo;s necessary for positivity.\n",
